text: Fatou Babou Diagne (born 20 January 1996) is a Senegalese basketball player for the Purdue Boilermakers and the Senegalese national team.Afrobasket.com profile She represented Senegal at the 2019 Women's Afrobasket.2019 Women's Afrobasket profile ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Centers (basketball) Category:Sportspeople from Thiès Category:Purdue Boilermakers women's basketball players Category:Senegalese expatriate basketball people in the United States Category:Senegalese women's basketball players
